{"tid":2072876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[檢討] 從罷工罷課公投人數不足 探討實體文宣重要性","createTime":"2020-06-21T02:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T11:58:58.000Z","uid":40431,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d228ea39dd0a3cc544c1a84d1479d04a110404","tid":2072876,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:35:22.000Z","msg":"學有啲巴打話齋，港共日講夜講話公投冇意義，叫人唔好參與之類，點都會知道有件咁嘅事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問題係知道有公投，未必知道咩人可以去投票 (投票資格)/去邊度投票 (投票地點)</span><br />\n<br />\n因為呢兩樣資訊，主要傳播途徑都係<br />\n1. Telegram Channel <br />\n2. 連登 <br />\n3. Facebook<br />\n<br />\n其中Facebook官方page「二百萬三罷聯合陣線」<span style=\"color: red;\">每個post最多都係得幾百人like/留言</span>，證明接觸面極度不足<br />\n<br />\n對比返上年比較多人嘅遊行/集會/三罷，最大嘅分別其他係實體文宣嘅消失，回想返612、616、818，甚至黎明行動，<span style=\"color: red;\">當時有鋪天蓋地嘅文宣，隨便一條隧道一條隧道都貼滿晒「邊日邊日，XX見」、「全民三罷」</span>，甚至有幾個商場入面貼到有連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n今時今日，仍然有手足竭而不捨咁貼文宣，<span style=\"color: red;\">但係隨住貼文宣風險增加/商場禁止貼嘢，當眼處嘅文宣/連儂牆幾乎都消失咗。</span>以往用連儂牆做社區通訊嘅途徑消失，活動宣傳嘅重心轉咗去網上<br />\n<br />\nFacebook本身係個唔錯嘅平台，但係往往一開，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔同嘅資訊充斥成個homepage</span>，當中可能好多都係重覆由唔同媒體報導嘅新聞 (蘋果、立場、RTHK、有線、仲有好多網媒)，<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣夾雜其中，碌碌吓skip咗嘅機會太高</span><br />\n<br />\nTelegram有個類似但係更嚴重嘅問題，除咗要join channel之外，一日千幾個新message，冇人會逐個追，更加唔會刻意碌返上去搵特定post<br />\n<br />\n實體文宣嘅作用始終冇辦法用電子文宣取代，要宣傳得好，需要某程度上嘅「重建連儂牆」。當然，過往咁貼文宣嘅可能性較低，但係可以諗一啲替代途徑，例如：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 印成賣旗般嘅貼紙俾人直接貼喺身上/朋友間互貼，人群造成一個流動嘅連儂牆<br />\n2. 落樓下，成棟樓嘅每個信箱都塞一張文宣</span><br />\n<br />\n以上只係拋磚，希望可以引玉，一齊思考多啲有創意嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n重燃抗爭熱度，需要從文宣做起"},{"pid":"062000353523fc0e46dc92cde95226ccb231391f","tid":2072876,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4d2ba5485c93dd0db08e1fb59ff83d620cef76","tid":2072876,"uid":261524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:36:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a419112a1c9420cf44203ec02576a9cf26ece8e9","tid":2072876,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:36:35.000Z","msg":"求推求討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2f4d7ec80f2e863d27dac276c80fb3b449ea42","tid":2072876,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"自push"},{"pid":"099a028d210af20d766e209ee374ccc61ec43492","tid":2072876,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fa0d52e43346862f67643eeb36a67fe70b54c6","tid":2072876,"uid":43062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:40:28.000Z","msg":"仲有Instagram <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都係要多啲實體文宣，連儂牆壽命好短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cada3aa864fe26110ac6bd5761a6064e9114e09","tid":2072876,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"想講，完全唔知有公投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到尋晚先知"},{"pid":"0ac9e65036d17bef1ced38450fd4cb9043a0730d","tid":2072876,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4fa0d52e43346862f67643eeb36a67fe70b54c6","tid":2072876,"uid":43062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:40:28.000Z","msg":"仲有In